     C           KEYW11    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KSEQN  20
     C                     KFLD           #KGROP  3
      *
     C           KEYW21    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KAPHZ  80
     C                     KFLD           #KAPBN  20
      *
     C           KEYW31    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KGROP  3
